sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Submit new workspace name
    Frontend->>API: PATCH /api/workspaces/{id}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and owner permission
    API->>DB: Load workspace
    DB-->>API: Workspace found
    API->>DB: Update workspace name
    DB-->>API: Workspace updated
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + updated workspace
    Frontend-->>Owner: Replace workspace label in UI
